00:00:43.315 --> 00:01:05.900
" I thought it was Southern California where this earthquake took place, but it was Northern California, just like the Lord showed me.

00:01:08.570 --> 00:01:35.920
I was praying over it and didn't even pay attention until people started sending me emails saying, "Hey, did you see this?

00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:51.570
" I heard about it, but I didn't think anything of it.

00:01:51.570 --> 00:01:58.800
Then I found out it was a 7.

00:01:58.800 --> 00:01:59.550
0.

