I was interceding, just praying in my normal daily routine, and the Lord told me, "Brandon, this was a warning before the major one.

00:02:25.995 --> 00:02:28.103
" This 7.

00:02:28.103 --> 00:02:40.320
1 that happened on 12/5 was a warning for what's coming.

