00:03:43.239 --> 00:03:53.004
On 12/5 of 2024, the earthquake took place.

00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:10.806
I thought there had to be something of significance to the number 1/5.

00:04:10.806 --> 00:04:35.575
Bo Polny is all into that; I'll have to ask him because he gets into all the numbers and see what he thinks.

00:04:35.575 --> 00:04:42.800
Maybe there's something more to it.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:05:26.515
If you all know more about 1/5 and if there's a spiritual significance to the numbers being 11 months into it—it happened almost on the exact day of five—I was just like, "Wow, Lord, that's interesting.

00:05:34.173 --> 00:05:46.245
" Then He said this was a warning; the major one is about to happen soon.

00:06:01.659 --> 00:06:17.900
I don't know exactly when, He did not give me that, but I know as we pray today, He will show us more.

00:06:17.900 --> 00:06:46.505
Whenever I told you about that visitation I had, I saw a massive quilt sewn down with golden thread that was quilted to the United States.

00:06:48.015 --> 00:07:06.840
