In another vision, I saw babies across the land with soiled diapers and flies surrounding them because the preachers were not teaching the truth.

00:09:12.839 --> 00:09:34.560
Then I saw that thread starting to be cut and pulled away; that hedge of protection was being lifted off that area.

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:59.222
Then the Lord showed me a massive earthquake that went from the San Francisco area through Portland and Seattle.

00:09:59.222 --> 00:10:11.308
