00:10:38.059 --> 00:10:57.110
I don't know if it was a pipeline, but everything from British Columbia up was on fire.

00:10:57.110 --> 00:11:10.600
Then the Lord showed me a massive tsunami wave caused when the land shifted.

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:30.491
It was like a landslide; that pressure caused a massive tsunami and it wiped out Japan.

00:11:30.491 --> 00:11:37.866
It was just covered in water.

00:11:44.950 --> 00:11:52.515
So, I thought it was really interesting that on 12/5, a substantial 7.

00:11:52.515 --> 00:12:00.760
1 earthquake happened on that same fault line.

00:12:00.760 --> 00:12:06.840
