00:13:40.251 --> 00:13:46.764
This will be an acceleration of that kind of stuff.

00:14:03.023 --> 00:14:05.909
The Lord warned me about this three or four days ago, and then it happened.

00:14:12.089 --> 00:14:13.600
I thought, "Boy, this is speeding up, Lord.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:24.257
" Sometimes what I see in the spirit takes years, but this happened quickly.

00:14:26.439 --> 00:14:44.080
